snippet.title: Amber Heard is 100% Borderline!
snippet.description:
There’s no “if” about it. The bit** truly suffers from Borderline Personality Disorder. Unfortunately, those associated with her seems to suffer more. It’s a real shame.

The sound is a bit shoddy at times, and I didn’t bother making sure the lighting (or myself) was aesthetically pleasing as it could have been, but hopefully the substance is still there; enough to make it worthwhile. Peace, and good luck to us all.


Follow up video: https://youtu.be/Og_iAWq_zCc
